        <p> Arrived in Hamburg, Steffi&rsquo;s Mama grabbed us thankfully and brought us home with the heavy backpacks.
            After a short afternoon sleep for Steffi, we went to the city and finally treated ourselves to pizza rolls and schnitzel. </p>
        <p> All in all, we had a wonderful 5.5 weeks of vacation. There were 7 flights, 3 countries, approx. 3000km with the motorhome, over 250km on foot, 8 dives, 5 day tours on the reef, 2 train journeys, 3700 photos and almost 8 hours of video material.
            We were even able to make a Hacken list on the &ldquo;seen in the wild&rdquo; with 2 other animal species.
            Rockwallabies on Magentic Island and the Cassowaries at the South Mission Beach.
            We only had to lift ourselves to the next visit to Australia.
            There were no major injuries than a slight sunburn.
            Nobody was sick in between. Even the weather almost always played along.
            It was just a good time.
            I hope that until the next visit to Australia will not pass for 4 years. </p>
